      "content": "For senior leadership, the look should scream \"powerful,\" which usually means sticking to classic, conservative styles. Men should opt for sharp, tailored suits in dark colors, and women should favor impeccably fitted professional wear. The goal is to look polished and authoritative, which often means avoiding anything too flashy or overly trendy. A well-maintained, understated appearance projects competence and seriousness in those high-stakes environments.",
