    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Got it. One thing I've been getting feedback on is how to handle more diverse hair textures or cultural styles. For example, if someone has very natural, textured hair or wears it in braids or locs, how would you advise them to style it to ensure they still fit that \"polished and authoritative\" look you mentioned? I want to make sure we aren't accidentally telling people they have to change who they are, but they still need to look professional for the board.",
