      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The best advice is to ensure whatever style they choose is neat, well-maintained, and controlled. If the hair is voluminous or highly textured, it needs to be managed so it doesn't look unruly or distracting in a formal setting. The focus should be on neatness and polish, not on forcing a specific texture, but the style must convey discipline. Ultimately, the presentation should look deliberate and professional, regardless of the natural texture.",
